summary: a comprehensive overview of the Project Management Institute (PMI) and its offerings, including certifications, training, events, and resources for project management professionals. PMI provides globally recognized certifications such as PMP, CAPM, and PMI-ACP, as well as agile certifications and micro-credentials. The organization offers various training options, world-class events, and resources to help professionals advance their careers and organizations. PMI also has a large global community, with local chapters and volunteer opportunities for members to connect and grow their networks.
